item.title: Just confused
item.dc:creator: @sk8rdude461 sk8rdude461
item.description:
@sk8rdude461 wrote:

Ashi:

Change the encoding

I helped him solve this in PM, and that was the solution.

For future readers that may come along: Your encoding should be UTF-8. Default is ANSI and typically it does work, but you can come along issues like this.
